52
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:30,060
Apologies for making you all worry.

53
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:33,730
My soul power has officially reached level 97.

54
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:35,760
Great!

55
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:37,860
Congratulations, Chief!

56
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:40,430
With the increase in the Chief's power,

57
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:42,560
the power of the entire Hao Tian Tribe

58
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,230
has reached a new level.

59
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,790
