82
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:41,760
and can only feel his approximate location.

83
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:43,860
Haishen Hall?

84
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:46,230
This was his target all along.

85
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,290
Tang San,

86
00:04:52,660 --> 00:04:53,760
you're very smart.

87
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,460
Haishen Mountain is the sacred land
for the God of the Ocean,

88
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:59,090
and the Haishen Hall is even more untouchable.

89
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,730
Once you hide in the hall,

90
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:03,360
I can't attack without inhibitions.

91
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:04,990
That's why

92
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:06,760
I need to stop you here.

93
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,390
Third Soul Skill,

94
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,530
God of the Ocean's Gaze!

95
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:44,130
She caught everyone at the same time!

96
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,960
Bo Sai Xi's control of spirit power

97
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,290
is far ahead of mine.

98
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:51,490
She can combine her strong spirit power
and soul power together,

99
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:54,690
and instantly transfer power
between different spaces.

100
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,330
Tang San,

101
00:05:56,130 --> 00:05:58,160
I know you are a very loyal person.

102
00:05:58,530 --> 00:06:00,360
Your friends are your support

103
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,760
but also your weakness.

104
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,890
You won't just sit back

105
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:07,560
and watch them be in trouble.

106
00:06:08,530 --> 00:06:09,260
San,

107
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:10,560
don't listen to her!

108
00:06:10,930 --> 00:06:12,160
As long as you persevere until the end,

109
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,030
we will all pass the test!

110
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,330
That's true.

111
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:17,060
But even if Tang San can persevere,

112
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:18,830
you guys might not be able to.

113
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:22,460
Fourth Soul Skill, Ocean of Annihilation!

114
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,030
What happened?

115
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:43,730
They are drowning.

116
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,030
Bo Sai Xi's Fourth Soul Skill

117
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,860
can create a confined space
filled with ocean water

118
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:52,730
and drown someone before they know it.

119
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:56,560
You don't have the right
to interfere with the Sixth Test.

120
00:06:57,330 --> 00:06:59,830
Whether or not to wait for thirty minutes

121
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,130
and watch his friends die

122
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:04,530
or properly face Bo Sai Xi

123
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:06,590
and take the test

124
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,930
is a choice that Tang San must make.

125
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:29,830
Brother,

126
00:07:30,330 --> 00:07:30,890
don't worry!

127
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,030
We are fine!

128
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:33,660
San,

129
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,230
