130
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:43,990
I've experienced this bone-chilling cold

131
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,390
in Slaughter City before.

132
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:48,560
This is

133
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,160
the feeling of intent to kill.

134
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,390
Senior Bo Sai Xi wants to kill me!

135
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,190
If this continues,

136
00:07:58,430 --> 00:07:59,530
