141
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:09,530
I won't hold back.

142
00:08:09,930 --> 00:08:14,330
Fifth Soul Skill, God of the Ocean's Summon,
Movement of Beasts!

143
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:16,130
Brother!

144
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,090
The attacks from these
ocean soul beasts' shadows

145
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:28,830
