267
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:22,630
God of the Ocean Seventh Test.

268
00:17:24,090 --> 00:17:25,490
Draw the magical weapon,

269
00:17:26,590 --> 00:17:28,430
God of the Ocean's Trident.

270
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:30,360
God of the Ocean's Trident?

271
00:17:31,330 --> 00:17:32,160
